#all methods, scenario 3 (now called scenario 2)
all_long %>%
  rename(Ensemble = ensemble) %>%
  filter(scenario==2) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=Method, y=MSE, group=Method, color=Ensemble)) +
  geom_boxplot() +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle=90)) +
  scale_x_discrete(labels = c("X - Complete Pool", "S - Complete Pool", "CF - Complete Pool", 
                              "X - Indicator", "S - Indicator", "CF - Indicator",
                              "X - Tree", "S - Tree", "CF - Tree",
                              "X - Forest", "S - Forest", "CF - Forest", 
                              "X - Lasso", "S - Lasso", "CF - Lasso", "Meta-Analysis")) +
  ggtitle("Boxplot of MSEs Across All Iterations for Scenario 2")
Error in rename(., Ensemble = ensemble) : object 'all_long' not found
